Developer Terms of Use
des:
Confused by insurance jargon? The Blue Shield of California skill provides answers to common questions, making your healthcare easier to understand and manage!

Say: “Alexa, enable Blue Shield of California” to get started.

A few things you can say:
 
Alexa, start My Blue Shield. Then:

• What’s the difference between an HMO and a PPO? 
• How do I get a virtual consultation? 
• When can I change plans?
• What can I buy with my FSA dollars?
• When is flu season?
• How do I add a dental plan?
• How does a deductible work?

Blue Shield of California is a not-for-profit health plan dedicated to providing access to high-quality health care at an affordable price.
